11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_DTLS_TRANSPORT_STATE_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_DTLS_TRANSPORT_STATE_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/dtls_transport_interface.h"
17#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21class RtcEventDtlsTransportState : public RtcEvent {
22 public:
23 static constexpr Type kType = Type::DtlsTransportState;
24
25 explicit RtcEventDtlsTransportState(DtlsTransportState state);
26 ~RtcEventDtlsTransportState() override;
27
28 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
29 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
30
31 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventDtlsTransportState> Copy() const;
32
33 DtlsTransportState dtls_transport_state() const {
34 return dtls_transport_state_;
35 }
36
37 private:
38 RtcEventDtlsTransportState(const RtcEventDtlsTransportState& other);
39
40 const DtlsTransportState dtls_transport_state_;
41};
42
43struct LoggedDtlsTransportState {
44 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_us; }
45 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_us / 1000; }
46
47 int64_t timestamp_us;
48 DtlsTransportState dtls_transport_state;
49};
50
51} // namespace webrtc
52
53#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_DTLS_TRANSPORT_STATE_H_
